com.facebook.litho.specmodels.model

Class DelegateMethodDescription

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.litho.specmodels.model.DelegateMethodDescription

  • public final class DelegateMethodDescription
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes the signature and other feature of a delegate method.

    We use method descriptions to refer to abstract methods defined in com.facebook.litho.ComponentLifecycle, so that we can define implementations that delegate to client-declared methods with annotated props.
